title: South Korea : e-commerce sales volume 2009 to 2018
yAxis: E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won. In total the number of data points it has is 10.
In general E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won has rose over the Year.
E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won is slightly increasing from 2009 to 2018.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won, of value 113.73 was reached at Year 2018
The lowest E-commerce sales volume in trillion Korean won, of value 20.64 was reported at Year 2009
